{"tid":1044310,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街，我間房有隻蚊阻住我訓教","createTime":"2019-03-02T20:00:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T18:55:37.000Z","uid":123335,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"aa57b8f9d7b880297a4d8b73220e053a10494c2a","tid":1044310,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T20:00:02.000Z","msg":"訓訓下教成日飛埋黎想吸我血 <br />\n但一落床又搵唔到佢<br />\n<br />\n岩岩終於搵到隻衰野<br />\n先發現原來啡啡地色，有保護色<br />\n唔怪得之咁難搵 <br />\n<br />\n然後ready 好一擊必殺果陣<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">竟然比隻衰蚊走甩咗！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n屌<br />\n依家隻野又唔見左 <br />\n好困擾呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cccd84c7d0140f7a44e1c60798406b540e9c5a2","tid":1044310,"uid":149844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T20:04:27.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆街到依家都仲捉緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"114815677571a57edd8c37f7b5365ae55096ff96","tid":1044310,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T20:06:10.000Z","msg":"買蚊帳啦"},{"pid":"d4be77bf1eb2dcd45db3558af17d46d385acff71","tid":1044310,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"2cccd84c7d0140f7a44e1c60798406b540e9c5a2","tid":1044310,"uid":149844,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T20:04:27.000Z","msg":"我都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仆街到依家都仲捉緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T20:10:45.000Z","msg":"我已經用左自己做引誘<br />\n暫時等左三個字都未出現<br />\n唉<br />\n好眼訓<br />\n照訓算<br />\n由佢咬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dd07f5c338b4d65ec505729291c9d59518a65e1","tid":1044310,"uid":123335,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T20:21:22.000Z","msg":"好消息！！！<br />\n